law.catch_line: Interpretation of KRS 211.680 to 211.686 and KRS 72.029 with respect to laws relating to coroners.
law.text: The provisions of KRS 211.680 to 211.686 and KRS 72.029 shall not be interpreted to limit, restrict, or otherwise affect any power, authority, duty, or responsibility imposed by any other provisions of law upon any coroner, but rather shall be interpreted to aid, assist, and complement the coroner in the performance of those statutory duties.
law.history: Created 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 347, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1996.
